$ sudo tlp setcharge 0 3 BAT1 -- X_BAT_PLUGIN_SIMULATE=framework
Error: battery BAT1 not present.
$ sudo tlp setcharge XYZZY ABCDE BAT1 -- X_BAT_PLUGIN_SIMULATE=framework
Error: battery BAT1 not present.
$ #
$ # --- tlp-stat
$ sudo tlp-stat -b -- X_BAT_PLUGIN_SIMULATE=framework | grep "charge_control_end_threshold"
