$ sudo tlp-stat -b -- X_BAT_PLUGIN_SIMULATE=framework X_THRESH_SIMULATE_READERR=1 | grep "charge_control_end_threshold"
/sys/class/power_supply/BAT0/charge_control_end_threshold   = (not available) [%]
